<div class="row w-100 my-10 px-9 d-none">
    <div class="d-flex flex-stack flex-wrap flex-md-nowrap card shadow p-8" style="background-color: #2577BC;">
        <!--begin::Content-->
        <div class="mb-5">
            <!--begin::Description-->
            <div class="fs-6 fs-lg-5 text-white fw-bold opacity-75">The kNOwWaste Knowledge Platform was developed through a Project Cooperation Agreement funding by UNEP on 2016. The platform provides data and information on holistic waste management to stakeholders in Asia and the Pacific region. The platform was developed with the following aims: generate and consolidate data or information on holistic waste management, transform data into easily comprehensible outputs for use by key stakeholders, map out and disseminate information on international waste management projects under the GPWM and UNEP projects as well as other international partners, and provide capacity building support through dissemination of data or information support for relevant stakeholders on holistic waste and waste management system.</div>
